**Core Domain**
User(user_id (PK), role, email, full_name)
Admin(admin_id (PK), user_id (FK→User))
Artist(artist_id, artist_name)
Records(record_id, title, genre, is_active)


**Circulation**
Checkout(checkout_id, user_id, record_id, checkout_date, return_date)



**Commerce**
Purchase(purchase_id, user_id, record_id, purchase_date, purchase_amount)
